{"tid":1240630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【621戰佢老母 】以 post 推 post ，盡小弟綿力大大力推！","createTime":"2019-06-18T11:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T10:15:48.000Z","uid":205482,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d52791afc41940999bc3544ad6988af3ad70d019","tid":1240630,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:46:44.000Z","msg":"【突發】共識已達！620 5pm 政府死線！621 罷工罷課罷市，二百萬人兵分三路！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1240180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1240180</a><br />\n<br />\n盡小弟綿力推 post, 香港等香港人救！<br />\n未完呀各位！不撤回，不罷休！宜家二百萬零一人全部都係自己人，我相信肯為香港付出嘅人係遠超過呢個數。四大訴求，香港人仲未追討成功啊！我哋唔需要林鄭下台，林鄭下台只會出現林鄭2.0！ 班手足被捕我真係唔好受，求求大家，爭取時間，睇睇以及廣傳呢個post 同埋準備好心情去抗爭。總之團結，勿分化、勿捉鬼、不篤灰、不抹黑、不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n抗爭宗旨：<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力，<br />\n百花齊放，殊途同歸，<br />\n槍口對外，絕不分化，<br />\n爭取自由，天經地義，<br />\n百萬加一，勿忘義士。<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢隨口噏"},{"pid":"77b5315ece4574b4a2568e1b26e81b0f87453788","tid":1240630,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:53:11.000Z","msg":"開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ad802ca330ce8d46da39403a97f9f2f4c4e58c","tid":1240630,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:52:48.000Z","msg":"香港人冇哂士氣嘅？"},{"pid":"2457cebb7fe8fa00189df0b2364993fc88e91c34","tid":1240630,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:11:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab310c355be83b2d51873d9f3dae21af49051fbb","tid":1240630,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2457cebb7fe8fa00189df0b2364993fc88e91c34","tid":1240630,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:11:35.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:14:31.000Z","msg":"謝謝巴打幫手推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gi